I reviewed the metric, trace, and log analyses. The strongest, earliest, and most sustained anomaly is a multi-minute, large-magnitude memory RSS spike on currencyservice-2 starting at 2022-03-21 13:32:00 (UTC+8), aligned with increased frontend traffic to currencyservice; other anomalies (adservice CPU) occurred later and are much smaller. Therefore the most likely single root cause is a container memory overload on currencyservice-2 at 2022-03-21 13:32:00.

